---
title: Sweet-and-Sour Pork over Bulgur Wheat
description: There’s something about sweet-and-sour sauce that keeps us coming back again and again (and again). This time, we’ve tossed it with crispy, golden brown pork and hearty bulgur for a healthier spin on a takeout favorite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/uk-sweet-and-sour-pork-family-d5c4abd8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sweet-and-sour-pork-90248c48.pdf
cuisine: Asian
time required: 35 minutes
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
